column6: Pollyanna Whittier is a young girl adopted by his wealthy aunt who was strict and cold spinster. She introduced to the people she met about one unique game that she played.Her kindness and politeness as well as her amazing acceptance upon the conditions can be seen obviously.

column6: As the reader can himself see from the stories in this book, the subject “Moral” is universal to every human being. Hence these stories are not just for any particular sect or the followers of particular faith, it is for the entire humanity, irrespective of there belief, culture, race, color or age.

monkeypen.com has already kick-started the ‘Free Book Project’ with 50 books. The books are professionally written and illustrated. Most of the stories are modernized and related with science and nature.
